Content.Text: <NAME_UNKOWN>Wake up. Wake up, already!

<FACE_WITCH><POS_LEFT><FACE_ANGRY>
<NAME_UNKOWN>How long are planning on sleeping for?
You're the one who called me here, and
now you're just sleeping?

<FACE_WITCH><POS_LEFT><FACE_NORMAL>
<NAME_UNKOWN>You made a house for me, right? Gathered
the blueprints for it and everything.
Does that ring any bells?

<FACE_WITCH><POS_LEFT><FACE_NORMAL>
<NAME_UNKOWN>That was the ritual that drew me forth.
And here I am, the beautiful and
glorious <BLUE>Witch Princess</BLUE>.
<PAGE>
<FACE_WITCH><POS_LEFT><FACE_NORMAL>That's why I'm here. So nice to meet
you, <MYNAME>!

<FACE_WITCH><POS_LEFT><FACE_NORMAL>
What do you need from me, then, <MYNAME>?
<PAGE>
You must have a very good reason for
having summoned me here.

<FACE_WITCH><POS_LEFT><FACE_NORMAL>
What? Nothing? You've got nothing? After
my big entrance and everything?
<PAGE>
<FACE_WITCH><POS_LEFT><FACE_ANGRY>Gaaaaah! What're you thinking?
<PAGE>
I hope you're ready to face the
consequences for this, <MYNAME>. The sin
of enraging me will cost you dearly.

<FACE_WITCH><POS_LEFT><FACE_NORMAL>
I'll turn you into a frog!
Dum-Da-Da-DAA!

<FACE_WITCH><POS_LEFT><FACE_NORMAL>
H-Harvest Goddess! What are you doing
here!

<FACE_GODDES><POS_RIGHT><FACE_ROUGH>
Oh, you didn't know? I'm the one
responsible for this land.

<FACE_WITCH><POS_LEFT><FACE_ANGRY>
Gah! I can't believe I've been called
here!

<FACE_GODDES><POS_RIGHT><FACE_ANGRY>
I can't believe it either. I hope you
aren't planning on hurting <MYNAME>!
<PAGE>
<MYNAME> is very special to me, and is
under my protection.

<FACE_WITCH><POS_LEFT><FACE_ANGRY>
What? No!

<FACE_GODDES><POS_RIGHT><FACE_NORMAL>
<MYNAME>, if this person ever tries to do
anything to you, just call me.
<PAGE>
I'll drive her off for you.

<FACE_GODDES><POS_RIGHT><FACE_ANGRY>
That's the way things are. Get on out of
here.

<FACE_WITCH><POS_LEFT><FACE_ANGRY>
As if! If I just back off now, then it
looks like I've lost!

<FACE_GODDES><POS_RIGHT><FACE_NORMAL>
Oh? You mean you haven't?

<FACE_WITCH><POS_LEFT><FACE_ANGRY>
Gah! How annoying are you?! That settles
it! I'm going to live here in town!
I can't leave while you're still here!

<FACE_GODDES><POS_RIGHT><FACE_ROUGH>
Oh really? Good luck with that. I need
to get some breakfast so I'll be leaving
now.

<FACE_WITCH><POS_LEFT><FACE_ANGRY>
I can't believe the Harvest Goddess is
here. There's something of a... past
between us. Argh, she's infuriating!

<FACE_WITCH><POS_LEFT><FACE_NORMAL>
I was going to punish you, but I've had
a change of heart. I'm going to live
here in town and cause trouble for her!

<FACE_WITCH><POS_LEFT><FACE_NORMAL>
I'll live in the house you built, so
make sure you bring me a nice
housewarming gift, you hear?

...This new resident looks like she's
quite a handful. I wonder if we'll be
be able to get along...
